Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:06.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回… 回锅肉套餐居然要八百元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有这钱都够买八杯杯面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,纸巾纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:12.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也给我来一张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:16.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,客人来了的话就实际地来招待一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:19.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 这不是杏子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:25.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 你怎么来这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然是来吃饭的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您想好要点什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是拉面加炒饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回锅肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:45.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看来客人您很有钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在小看我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拉面加炒饭 还有回锅肉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我说杏子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:04:01.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她是这么说 但是跟熟人可以随便一点的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 这家伙就不是什么上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是个普通人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你小看我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你怎么会在这儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔阿姨收养了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那还挺好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:25.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:27.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚被收养就干活 还挺不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏和她真是没法比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能再想了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:39.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你来做做收银吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:44.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟我刚才做的一样就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然合计要1500元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你很快就会知道 这没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:05.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(737,0)\c&H8EE4EB&\3c&H52808B&\fn萝莉体 第二版\fs80\frz18.26\pos(1020,436)}钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子看到太多钱 人僵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子啊 洗得怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一次性筷子扔掉就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不都是洗洗再用的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 不用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:26.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:32.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前茂叔教我这筷子洗洗就能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在杏子的心中活着很多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我说过这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但感觉一直在不断否定她的过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也要继续干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,工作都结束了 就跟平常一样就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:56.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 我放好洗澡水了你去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道该怎么洗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是冷水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:13.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一直都是在公园洗的 没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在可以用热水了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:24.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在可以随便用电灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:31.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天还不太明白 原来这是我的房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一个家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安叔 茂叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:46.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我今后也会加…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:53.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.93,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)\shad0\blur5\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(410,770)}超能力女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.98,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(487,900)\shad0\blur5\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1518,748)}超能力女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,提问 有「パン」但吃不了的「パン」是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}フライパン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,除了「平底锅」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「住一宿吃顿饭」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}一宿いっぱん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:03.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那还是吃了啊 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「铁板」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}「てっぱん」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:04.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有「安全裤」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:04.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\pos(1018,998)}見せパン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有熊猫也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}「パンダ」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:07.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 新田 新田！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:14.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,上课总是睡觉 我今天一定饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是来学校干什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:19.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为你老是这样 考试也总不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说新田 你在认真听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这现在表情是什么态度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我也不是想生气才生气的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:31.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是狠下心来才对你生气的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,画出东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:40.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再多给我点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还要给其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真小气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:46.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,态度真差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,学校真是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说想去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:57.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是无聊 就努力创造点乐趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近要举行学生会成员竞选了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想参加的人在下次参加课外活动的时候去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:06.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又流口水了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳你这么认真 考不考虑加入学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定是不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,纱夜你也挺不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看你还戴着眼镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在说笑话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:21.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会决定某些事情的预算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也制定一些新校规
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比如让不让看漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:30.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说这是学校里的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,掌权者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是学生会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:37.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说老大是学生会 倒不如说学生会长才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这说的也太随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系了 毕竟她是雏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,掌权者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老子终于获得了权利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:48.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老子就是老大 规则都是老子来定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 我居然没办法反抗权力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,疼 疼 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:09:00.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有人想竞选学生会成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有其他人了吗 没了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:13.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:22.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那… 新田竞选学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:26.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说雏 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:30.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成为学生会长 手握大权
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:31.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪健吾你说了那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:35.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怪我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:38.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 在这之前 第一年只能当委员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:39.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还挺有趣的 静观其变怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,纱夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:48.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 下个星期学校早会上要发表演讲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:49.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:54.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我教师生涯里第一次听这句话会感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:03.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷老师的班里还有这么积极参加竞选的学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:07.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他嗤笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 雏你在写什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:16.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,参加竞选的人要进行演讲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:17.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我睡觉也没人对我发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能多提供饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:24.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:25.20,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz8.393\move(949.333,218.666,959.999,306.667,5,4926)}希望我睡觉也没人对我发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:25.20,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz8.96\move(991.333,366.666,993.333,460,5,4926)}希望能多提供饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:25.20,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz10.54\move(1389.333,762.667,1401.334,854.666,5,4926)}没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:32.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 你这不过是把想法罗列了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:35.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好写演讲原稿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你参加了学生会长的竞选
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 看来我应该是睡昏头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么来着 说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我参加了学生会长的竞选
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然是睡醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:58.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说一年级能当学生会长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:00.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的学校都是这么干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:03.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别人说我的演讲稿不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.93,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz18.75\pos(788,456)}希望我睡觉也没人对我发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.93,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\pos(728,570)\frz18.49}希望能多提供饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.93,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz20.75\pos(1069.333,640.667)}没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是荒唐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:09.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦死了 你自己考虑考虑呗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:16.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是新田说的努力创造点乐趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 事情变得比较麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:27.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这无论如何也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏她都已经这么努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这废什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你得尽力帮她啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 让咱们的顾问律师来改改怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:44.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是组里的人遇上条子找麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:50.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是这种程度的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 到底出什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还真叫来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:01.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来将进行学生会候选人的演讲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:04.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一年三班 新田雏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:11.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了 感觉好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:12.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底会变成怎么样的演讲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:23.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一年三班的新田雏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我当选上学生会长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:30.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一年级生只能当书记或者会计的候选人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我当选上学生会长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:37.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}彻底无视了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:40.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我将努力改善伙食
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我校的伙食在二十五年间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一直委托给朝香伙食中心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是包括邻近的学校在内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都与其签订了长年的协定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:55.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其内部情况 从成本、质量这两个方面来看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,实在也不能说是处于很好的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:02.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 以竞争投标的方式来选择其他公司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:04.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,致力于降低成本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}同时得以据此提高伙食的质量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:06.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在讲很一本正经的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:14.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让学生对伙食感到安全性 还有营养这一方面也能有所改善吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,读到这里深吸一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(860,602)\shad0\bord2\frz27.28\fn思源宋体 CN\b1\c&H535157&\3c&HFFFFFF&}读到这里深吸一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:21.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,深吸一口气？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:24.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 比起伙食改善
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:28.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饱餐一顿之后 无论如何都会变得晕晕欲睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前刚才那句话什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:34.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里举起手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:35.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}这不是没举起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让大家可以午后的打个小盹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:36.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}继续读下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,将会引入午睡时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 引入的方法是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉时不时会冒出点东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:47.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至于午睡的效果 请看接下来的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:47.97,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz31.73\c&H727272&\pos(698,758)}是否感到午觉有效
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:47.97,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(632,692)\frz34.22}有效 79%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:47.97,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\c&HFFFFFF&\frz30.55\pos(542,412)}没感觉 21%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:47.97,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz30.53\c&H79787C&\bord2\pos(1140,586)}引入午睡制度后的成绩变化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:47.97,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz29.79\pos(846,188)\c&H000000&\bord2}引入前 引入后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:52.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看了这个之后想必大家就一目了然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 资料在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:58.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以上 我的演讲完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里鞠个躬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:08.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然槽点有点多 不过真是了不起的演讲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:12.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 只是她说的完全超出了学生会的职能范围了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,600)\fn思源宋体 CN\shad0\bord1\c&H505052&\3c&HFFFFFF&}学生会成员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 这也是一开始就定好的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:30.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能成为学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,成了还得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行啦 今天就去外面吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么想吃的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:42.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鲑鱼子盖饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏一次都没去过学生会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 会长嘱咐我今天必须把她带过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你稍微来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你来就行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想着这样会比较容易看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快一点的话就赶不上开店了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里摆成这样比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,确实效率提高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,关于运动会的请愿书…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经整理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:20.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:23.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都没来 我还想着发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好啊 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我是三岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:28.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:29.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下来也能过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:35.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正新田她也不来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当代理书记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到 学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:44.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,welcome……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:49.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诗子小姐 下次跟我一起去吃顿饭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:53.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 怎么办好呢 我工作很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近不也没什么大事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你不在店里也没差啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我的店哦 我在就很重要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全的花瓶宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诗子小姐完全不为所动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说又能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟别人倾述一下会比较轻松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 说是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:22.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 怎么说了句最不像你会说的话top10
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,电视上说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:30.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:34.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 我要跟雏商量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:35.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱话题？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有没有自尊心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 新田先生他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是有邀请诗子小姐去约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但据说不顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:46.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:49.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是如果进展顺利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诗子小姐可能会成为你妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来小雏的妈妈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田他好像也有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:04.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:08.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 两个人进展不顺利的时候要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:11.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你问我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:15.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 恋爱什么的还太早了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:19.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 到底是怎么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\an8}太平间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:25.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏 那么早就没了妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:27.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我做不到什么大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会加油哦 会给你应援的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:42.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要若无其事地讲些新田先生的好话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:44.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能地让诗子小姐愿意和他去约会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:45.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小雏也一起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:57.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田说他想跟诗子你约会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:00.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我们根本就没达成共识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:04.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 派小孩来游说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:06.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田还真是干了件了有品的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:09.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,随着误会 对新田先生的评价也下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:13.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的哦 其实是小雏感受到了你们俩之间的氛围之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:14.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 她感受不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:20.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏 新田先生的优点！优点！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田是个好人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:26.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会给我做饭 什么都会买给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种就是个好利用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 去约会一次也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:39.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,工作上诗子小姐不在也完全不会困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去就行了吧！我去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}电视机前的乖孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田和美佳都是黑头发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:57.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}义史8岁 美佳6岁 拿着苍蝇拍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:58.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在学习妈妈相关知识
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:03.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为诗子会成为我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:06.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事这个神展开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:09.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她说愿意和我约会了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自作主张做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上一直久攻不下也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:20.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为有孩子只会是我的减分点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 反而可以成为利器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好啊 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就到约会的时间了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:53.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:56.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我要留在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说这次都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:05.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 明明你都住院了我却一个人去享受也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也想要妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:11.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:17.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:23.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你等着 下次再见的时候妈妈也会一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:29.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实收到了 你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我已经给你看过我哭的丑态了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:37.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是直到能与妈妈相见那时为止 你可先别让我看你的哭脸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的眼泪 一定是喜悦的眼泪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:42.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你约定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我是个混黑道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:48.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会让你和诗子小姐 笑容满溢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搭建一个温暖的家庭的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我哦雏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:55.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,男子汉新田义史
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就在此处 一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 拒绝他了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上小雏也黏他黏得很紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:36.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的新田也光在讲雏的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就让人觉得根本无法进入这两人其中啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:42.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就跟他说了离过一次婚还带着孩子的男人不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这说法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:46.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种程度的话还是说清楚比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:50.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,该说是清楚呢还是决绝呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:22:00.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 我是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:04.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 久等啦 笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:06.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来 笑一个
