Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:44.06,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}どうかして上がるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:51.00,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}「ギャラじゃねー癖に」と笑う
